  <brief_title>Optimal Dosing For Low-Dose Aspirin Chemoprophylaxis For VTE Following Total Joint Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimal Dosing For Low-Dose Aspirin Chemoprophylaxis For Venous Thromboembolism Following Total Joint Arthroplasty - A Multi-center Prospective Randomized Control Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
