  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research study is attempting to answer the question of whether 81 mg aspirin once daily
      is as effective as 81 mg aspirin twice daily in preventing blood clots after total joint
      replacement surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
